<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.sccjr.ac.uk/pubs/User-Views-of-Punishment-The-comparative-experience-of-short-term-prison-sentences-and-communitybased-punishments/284">User Views of Punishment: The comparative experience of short term prison sentences and community-based punishments</a> Research Report by <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.sccjr.ac.uk">The Scottish Centre for Crime and Justice Research</a></li>
</ul>
